snippet.title: Mega CD Longplay [142] Yumimi Mix (JP)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

I though this would be an adventure game, but it's an interactive movie more than anything.

00:00:00 Path to Ending 1

There are 3 endings, during the main gameplay got (the good?) one, and the other 2 depend on the choices you make at 01:43:10

02:05:50 Path to ending 2

The third ending you get if you chose to sing during the ending 2 gameplay at 02:08:43

02:25:48 Path to ending 3 -
